fields.text: This course provided an excellent introduction to environmental conservation. The content was well-structured and easy to follow.
I learned a lot about marine conservation. The course covered a wide range of topics, but I would have liked more hands-on activities.
Great insights on sustainable agriculture! The instructor was very knowledgeable, and the resources provided were valuable.
The course on wildlife conservation was informative, but the pacing was a bit slow. I enjoyed learning about different conservation strategies.
This course on environmental policy was eye-opening. The case studies were particularly useful in understanding real-world applications.
Good overview of environmental conservation. I appreciated the detailed explanations, but some topics could have been explored in more depth.
